data.description: Welcome to this charming single-family home! Situated on a sizable .23 acre lot with mature trees and RV parking with hookups! This property offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Step into the kitchen, where you'll find sleek granite countertops and an abundance of natural light that fills the space. The plant shelves add a touch of personality, allowing you to create a unique and inviting ambiance in your open living room. Step outside into the spacious yard, offering endless possibilities for creating your dream backyard oasis. With a partial cinder block wall and an uncovered patio, the outdoor space offers both privacy and relaxation. Best of all, there's no HOA, giving you the flexibility and freedom to truly make this house your home.
